headline: IVZ Stock Gains on Q4 Earnings Beat as AUM, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: Invesco shares rise in the pre-market trading after Q4 adjusted EPS beat estimates, with revenues up 8.8% y/y and AUM hitting a record $2.17T.
